Widget Studio Desktop Installer Mock Package
==========================================

This file simulates the Widget Studio .msi installer package in the web preview mode.

Steps to Run:
1. Copy this file into your project workspace.
2. In production, this file is compiled using tauri-bundle into a fully operational Windows Installer (.msi).
3. The Tauri runtime launches the application natively with low footprint overlays.

For support, visit: http://localhost:8000/
